data.description: Nestled in the heart of Cabot sits this wonderful family home with convenient access to local amenities, schools, shopping, and dining options, all within a quaint neighborhood. This home features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, you'll enjoy having two separate living spaces that cater to all your needs as well as a large kitchen and separate dining area. At the end of a long day, dive into relaxation and unwind in your own backyard oasis complete with a pool that's perfect for cooling off on warm days and hosting unforgettable poolside gatherings. This home comes with solar panels that are completely paid for.  YOU DON'T WANT TO MISS THIS ONE!
